name: SXZ Trolls [ Warcraft ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with Clip Skip 2.

Sample images was generated with Luma and AOM2

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5
3. badhandv4

Strength 0.6-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Male Orc: 1boy, hewowtroll, grey skin
Female Orc: 1girl, shewowtroll, grey skin

Please note that fangs / tusks may not appear on some models.

Skin color: dark grey, green, dark
Eye color: red, blue, yellow, purple

Also you may improve it with muscular, glowing eyes, face paint, fangs, tusks

When you using 1boy, hewowtroll or 1girl, shewowtroll add opposite in negative prompt.
